	   <tr><td colspan=2> Ok, i just wanted to add something. Personally, whenever im bored, or i want to get together with some friends i go to the arena zone and bully around people for a lil bit &gt;=) Here are some lil tricks i learned from my experiences there...<br><br>1) ALWAYS stay in the Arena itself, if you leave and a dot kills you, you lose XP, TELL THIS TO EVERYONE YOU ARE DUELING!<br>2) Cast levitate on you, then climb up the wiz spires whenever you want to escape. Its a very mean trick, but it works VERY well against both casters and tanks.<br>3) The arena is a PvP area, if you dont want to get killed then dont go. It's nothing personal when someone kills you, and as long as you stay INSIDE the arena you wont lose any XP, so PLEASE dont fly off the handle when you die. (notice i said when).<br><br>I have had a great number of very entertaining times here. One of which me, and about 8 other level 30ish people took on a 58 necro thats in my guild. We all died at least once killing him, but we did in the long run. This experience made us wiser then our years as far as strategies for poth PvP and even dragon raids! SO go kill some people and let everyone know the wrath of us shaman!<br><br>Nitsujlak Barshemguud Ogre Shammy of war!<br>Prexus Server<br>Please rate my posts, i like input on my advice =)<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
